FULL.DESC: Various small potentiometers for set-and-forget applications

V_REG MIC5205 Standard 3.3V, 5V, and Adjustable 150mA LDO voltage regulator in SOT-23 layout. Micrel part MIC5205. BP (by-pass) pin is used to lower output noise with 470pF cap, may be left open. On the adjustable version BP is used to set output.
